These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, alhambra, vegafina, aristoff
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, almond-milk, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, time-travel, zombie
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, photography, board-games, gardening
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, blood-red, pink, green
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, balloon-flower, daisy, sunflower
City: liverpool, boston, colone, paris
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is not the person traveling to boston##6
 4. the person traveling to colone is not the alhambra-smoker##6
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
 6. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 7. the person traveling to paris is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is not the aristoff-smoker##6
10. the person drinking coffee is the person traveling to boston##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person traveling to liverpool##1
12. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
13. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
14. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
15. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
16. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to paris##7
17. the person who growssunflower is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
18. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
19. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who growszinnia##7
20. the person who likes blood-red is not the aristoff-smoker##6
21. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar          | bolivar      | aristoff   | alhambra     | vegafina |
| Beverage           | coffee | fanta   | water    | almond-milk     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie       | time-travel | horror   | mystery   |
| Hobby   | board-games      | gardening     | fishing | photography    |
| Color           | blood-red   | green       | pink  | ivory       |
| Flower         | zinnia     | balloon-flower     | daisy | sunflower   |
| City     | boston          | colone      | paris     | liverpool      |

